class="el-p"><p dir="auto">In this project, well attach the ESP32-CAM to a pan and tilt stand with two SG90 servo motors. With a pan and tilt camera stand, you can move the camera up, down, to the left, and the right this is great for surveillance. The ESP32-CAM hosts a web server that shows video streaming and buttons to control the servo motors to move the camera.<br>
